### Online group classes 

Schedule for the courses available for sign up in July-November

Price per lesson (45 min.) in a group of 6-8 students is 109 DKK

A1 Level    Duration 12 weeks     Two classes per week        2X2 lessons * 45 min            Homework load 3-4 hours per week
A2 Level    Duration 12 weeks     Two classes per week        2X2 lessons * 45 min            Homework load 3-4 hours per week

B1.1 Level  Duration 10 weeks     One class per week          1X4 lessons * 45 min            Homework load 3-4 hours per week
B1.2 Level  Duration 10 weeks     One class per week          1X4 lessons * 45 min            Homework load 3-4 hours per week

B2.1 Level  Duration 10 weeks     One class per week          1X4  lessons * 45 min           Homework load 4 hours per week
B2.2 Level  Duration 10 weeks     One class per week          1X4  lessons * 45 min           Homework load 4 hours per week

C1 Level    Duration 11 weeks     One class per week          1X4 lessons * 45 min            Homework load 8 hours per week
